Preface

This document describes the Realtek Telephone API (TAPI) for the telephony features is used in Realtek VoIP products.
In this guide, it also provides example programs to demonstrate the various features of Realtek TAPI.

Document Organization

This document focuses on two main issues of the programming guide, namely the TAPI usage and the general features description.

  • Modules
    This presents all VoIP modules. Expand down to see a more detailed description of the TAPI and usage.

  • Files

  • Examples
